results.name: Inverse of sequence A035513 considered as a permutation of the nonnegative integers.
link: Index entries for sequences that are permutations of the natural numbers
maple: Digits := 30 : A035513 := proc(n,k) local tau ; tau := (sqrt(5)+1)/2 ; combinat[fibonacci](k+1)*floor(n*tau)+(n-1)*combinat[fibonacci](k) ; end: A035513flat := proc(N) local r,c,k,np,n ; n := 1 : k := 1 : for np from 2 to N do n := n+1 : k := k-1 : if k = 0 then k := n: n := 1: fi ; od ; A035513(n,k) ; end: a035513 := [] : a := -1 : nmax := 300 : for n from 1 to nmax do a035513 := [op(a035513),A035513flat(n)] : od : printf("0, ") ; n := 1: while true do if member(n,a035513,'a') then printf("%d, ",a) ; else break ; fi ; n := n+1 : od: # _R. J. Mathar_, Jun 26 2007
